            <guid>https://li-tann.github.io/blog/2023/03/07/word-check-mark</guid>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Mar 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[在word输入2611, 按ALT+X, 即可生成“框内打勾✅”的特殊字符。]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在word输入<code>2611</code>, 按<code>ALT</code>+<code>X</code>, 即可生成“框内打勾✅”的特殊字符。</p>]]></content:encoded>
